WEBVTT

00:03.838 --> 00:07.258
COACH BURIES A GRUDGE

00:08.844 --> 00:12.304
- Hey, everybody.
- How are you doing?

00:15.891 --> 00:20.937
- Surprise, surprise.
- Looky there. What's the occasion?

00:21.104 --> 00:26.484
Just a little peace offering.
I'm trying to make up for last night.

00:26.651 --> 00:29.361
You should feeI bad about that.

00:29.528 --> 00:34.241
No guy likes to be laughed at
at that particular moment.

00:35.950 --> 00:39.746
I couldn't help it.
You had that look on your face

00:39.913 --> 00:43.875
and for just a second,
you looked like a flounder.

00:45.126 --> 00:48.545
- Maybe it was the light.
- Apology accepted.

00:48.753 --> 00:52.174
But this better be a damn good gift,
I'll tell you that.

00:52.340 --> 00:56.595
I'll be darned. It's a sweater?

00:56.761 --> 01:00.015
An Icelandic snowflake
rag wooI sweater.

01:00.182 --> 01:03.100
I saw it in a catalogue. I had to get it.

01:03.267 --> 01:07.854
- Thank you. I love it. It's great.
- Put it on right now.

01:08.021 --> 01:14.027
I like to live with a piece of clothing
for a little while before I wear it.

01:14.194 --> 01:18.823
Come on. I know it's unusuaI.
It looks different when it's on.

01:18.990 --> 01:20.949
One person laughs...

01:21.116 --> 01:26.456
He will be exhibiting his own insecurity
and lack of taste.

01:26.623 --> 01:28.832
I just hate looking silly.

01:30.334 --> 01:34.170
Sam is about to modeI
his new sweater for us.

01:34.337 --> 01:39.883
- Look, Cliffie, goose bumps.
- Nothing in my horoscope about that.

01:41.093 --> 01:45.514
- Does it fit all right?
- It fits OK. Come in and take a look.

01:45.681 --> 01:50.101
You come out and show everyone
what a fashion plate you are.

01:50.268 --> 01:53.687
Believe me, not so much as a smirk.

